{"tid":1832097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何栢良批政府防疫落後　籲市民勿以為沙士歷史不會重現","createTime":"2020-01-21T02:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T04:50:47.000Z","uid":263197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08a17272640403e74eec7c6a9ebcf6bd694af990","tid":1832097,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"來源：RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503899-20200121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503899-20200121.htm&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6lHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=d96b790f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503899-20200121.htm&h=2eee29e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503899-20200121.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案飆升，疫情蔓延至多個城市，包括與香港一河之隔的深圳。由武漢乘搭飛機抵港的旅客，凌晨起需填寫健康申報表。<br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">政府應對疫情的措施落後於形勢</span></span>，讓人感覺是措手不及，防疫宣傳嚴重不足，認為除了要求填寫健康申報表，政府應該採取更多防疫措施，不要等到香港出現首宗確診個案才開始行動。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良出席本台節目《千禧年代》時又說，<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">內地官方公布的數據很少，他知道的資料不會比一般人多</span></span>，由於臨床數據少，如果香港出現確診個案，只能參考類似的疾病處方藥物，例如沙士、中東呼吸綜合症等；最差的情況是病毒一傳入香港，就已經有數十人感染，出現「超級傳播」的情況，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提醒市民不要以為17年前的沙士慘痛教訓歷史一定不會重現</span></span>。"},{"pid":"047db1c2c7c605434c5717e02ecccb0b5a63bd0d","tid":1832097,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"History repeat itself.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbe1fa43e3c9104d0882f63c5c6cce518ced4c8","tid":1832097,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}